{"tid":578155,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"入黎討論下「學習方法」","createTime":"2018-03-02T11:13:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-01T19:11:59.000Z","uid":86549,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"b428d662cfa6cc9ebffb0239e3a946cb3c93fca8","tid":578155,"uid":86549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T11:13:12.000Z","msg":"Dse雞都可以參考下<br />\n但呢度想集中講「學習」並非「考試」<br />\n<br />\n通常講到學野我諗大家都唔會否定「理解」既必要性<br />\n關於理解 明白 understand 等等既字眼其實諗諗下覺得好抽象<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲可以講下點先知道自己係真真正正「理解」一樣野？"},{"pid":"e3eee029eb7e3e61148f4fce40d570444cf422e7","tid":578155,"uid":70760,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T11:19:03.000Z","msg":"現實角度學完之後可以講得番出黎俾自己聽, 你present了得講埋俾一個門外漢聽, 都算理解<br />\n<br />\n至於理解既知識夠唔夠全面,又是否為真,就哲學方面了"},{"pid":"d1377e4f4cf2179b4b95713b7e643a9148c95eb5","tid":578155,"uid":86549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3eee029eb7e3e61148f4fce40d570444cf422e7","tid":578155,"uid":70760,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T11:19:03.000Z","msg":"現實角度學完之後可以講得番出黎俾自己聽, 你present了得講埋俾一個門外漢聽, 都算理解<br />\n<br />\n至於理解既知識夠唔夠全面,又是否為真,就哲學方面了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T11:26:30.000Z","msg":"真唔真就算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但夠唔夠全面又點界定？<br />\n你可以背書咁背番比自己聽 但咁算唔算理解？"},{"pid":"dc9bbf78365efe8fc881b23f5b71e4237191582d","tid":578155,"uid":86549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T12:00:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"755f4a4b45f535cb0f2c1be15939ad4d2b3b886e","tid":578155,"uid":86549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T13:17:08.000Z","msg":"入黎問下野討論下都好丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4982402f72de3cfe9636b76de0e94ebb4ae244e1","tid":578155,"uid":36158,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T13:18:56.000Z","msg":"我認為可以做到上推下切 舉一反三 游刀有刃就係理解左"},